text: Heya Chris, you ready for today? I’ve never been to Bring your own animation before, is there usually a good mix of industry people to give you critique, or has it usually been mainly animators and 3D modellers?

Hell yeah I'm ready, normally it's pretty heavily skewed to the animation side of things, which is why I'm pushing for more wonderful comp people to come along, this is literally month 2 of comp feedback and the first month I've advertised it so who knows what the turnout will be like.
Ah good to know, also glad you’re trying to get it more broad to help more people interested in different parts of the industry. I’ll probably get there around 7, hopefully no later.
Sounds good to me, I'm going straight from work so I should be there
Looks like I’ll be a lot earlier then I thought, walking up to the pub now. Are you there yet?
